</P>
<P>
 * WHEN AND WHERE: 8 p.m. Saturday, Mount Cross Lutheran Church, 102 Camino 
Esplendido, Camarillo. Also, 4 p.m. Sunday, San Buenaventura Mission, Ventura. 
</P>
<P>
 * HOW MUCH: $18, $15 senior citizens and students; family and group rates. 
</P>
<P>
