<DOCNO> LA121594-0011 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 108115 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 15, 1994, Thursday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
