County and others in the future is to make the municipality publish its 
investments in a general circulation newspaper on a regular basis for the 
taxpayers to see. Then make a lengthy jail sentence and heavy fine for any 
irregularities in disclosure. This would almost eliminate this problem without 
government intervention. 
</P>
<P>
 RICHARD CAUBLE 
</P>
<P>
 Westminster 
