<HEADLINE>
<P>
COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTH GATE; CITY COLLECTING FOOD FOR NEEDY FAMILIES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The city is conducting its annual Christmas Food Drive through Wednesday. 
</P>
<P>
 City employees will donate canned foods, dairy products and dry goods that 
will be used to assemble food baskets. City staff members deliver the food 
baskets to needy families in South Gate. To qualify, residents must sign up 
with local churches. 
</P>
<P>
 For information, contact Veronica Lopez of the Building and Safety Department: 
(213) 563-9513. 
</P>
