Martians," a comic musical by the Golden State Children's Theatre Friday, Dec. 
16, at 7:30 p.m. and Saturday, Dec. 17, at 2 p.m. at the La Mirada Theatre for 
the Performing Arts. $6. (714) 994-6310. 
