</P>
<P>
 The Wayne Gretzky and Friends Tour wound up its European trip tih an 8-5 
victory over a German all-star team at Frieburg, Germany. . . . The 1994 
champion of bass angling's top event was among the passengers presumed killed 
when an American Eagle commuter plane crashed in North Carolina.Bryan Kerchal, 
23, of Newtown, Conn., won the BASS Masters Classic at High Rock Lake, N.C., in 
July. 
