<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA121594-0339 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 108443 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 15, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 56; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
