<P>
 Euro Disney to Cut Prices: Although the company said the number of visitors to 
the Euro Disney theme park outside Paris -- battered by two years of losses and 
poor attendance -- has risen this year, it has announced plans to cut admission 
prices next spring. It also said Saudi Prince Al Waleed ibn Talal ibn Abdulaziz 
