</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 HMO California said Wednesday that it has agreed to be acquired by Employers 
Health Insurance Co., a unit of Emphesys Financial Group Inc. of Green Bay, 
Wis.Terms of the purchase by Employers Health, the nation's 10th-largest group 
health insurance company, were not disclosed. 
